{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Mengenal Berbagai Jenis Film Horor","content":"<p>Ketika kita menyaksikan film horor untuk pertama kalinya, tak dipungkiri bahwa kita kerap meng-generalisasikan <em>genre</em>-nya. Alias, mau film horor yang dimaksud menampilkan zombie, drakula, paranormal, kesurupan, dan yang lainnya, kita kerap menganggapnya film horor saja.</p>\n<p>Padahal layaknya <em>genre </em>drama, horor juga memiliki variasi sub-<em>genre</em>. Nah bagi kamu-kamu yang <em>fans </em>berat horor namun, belum terlalu familiar dengan varian sub<em>-genre </em>yang dimaksud, berikut adalah 15 jenis film horor<em> </em>terkenal diantaranya.</p>\n<p>Oh ya sebelum kita membahas, perlu saya ingatkan lagi dikarenakan kita akan membahas berbagai jenis film horor, BERHATI-HATILAH! Karena artikel ini akan menampilkan foto-foto yang mungkin akan membuat kaget atau membuat kalian jadi muntah (<em>disturbing)</em>.</p>\n<p>Kalau sudah jelas, <em>let’s begin this fright &amp; gore fest shall we?</em></p>\n<h2>Berbagai Jenis Film Horor</h2>\n<h3><strong>Action Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52415\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52415\" data-attachment-id=\"52415\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/01-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52415\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Film Freedonia\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52415\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Film Freedonia</p></div></p>\n<p>Sesuai namanya, <em>genre </em>ini mencampurkan elemen kengerian, ketegangan dengan adegan-adegan aksi <em>badass </em>menggunakan senjata dan kejar-kejaran intens ala film <em>action</em>.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Alien, Predator, Resident Evil, From Dusk Till’ Dawn, Feast</em></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-resident-evil-transformers-kritik/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sering Dihujat, Film Resident Evil dan Transformers Tetap Laris</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Body Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52416\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52416\" data-attachment-id=\"52416\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/02-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52416\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: IndieWire\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52416\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: IndieWire</p></div></p>\n<p>Film horor ini lebih menampilkan rasa ngeri dan ngilu-nya melalui tampilan anggota-anggota tubuh yang mengelupas, lepas dari tubuh atau “sambung-tempel” ke bagian tubuh lain.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>The Fly, The Thing, American Mary</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Comedy Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52417\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52417\" data-attachment-id=\"52417\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/03-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52417\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: io9-Gizmodo\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52417\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: io9-Gizmodo</p></div></p>\n<p>Kalau diipikir lagi, mana yang satu adalah <em>genre </em>untuk menakut-nakuti, sedangkan yang satu adalah <em>genre </em>untuk membuat tertawa terbahak-bahak. Mana mungkin bisa menyatu bukan?</p>\n<p>Tapi kenyataannya <em>genre </em>ini eksis hingga detik ini dan sukses besar membuat kita takut dan terbahak-bahak secara bersamaan.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Shaun of the Dead, Beetlejuice, Zombieland, Ghostbusters</em></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/game-ghostbusters-world-pengalaman-menangkap-hantu-secara-nyata/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Game Ghostbusters World, Pengalaman Menangkap Hantu Secara Nyata</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Holiday Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52418\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52418\" data-attachment-id=\"52418\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/04-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52418\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: TheWrap\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52418\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: TheWrap</p></div></p>\n<p>Film horor yang menampilkan peristiwa menyeramkan (umumnya pembunuhan sadis) yang terjadi di sekitar musim liburan atau hari-hari non liburan yang kerap dirayakan oleh seluruh warga luar negeri sana.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Silent Night, Black Christmas, Halloween, My Bloody Valentine, April Fool’s Day</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Natural Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52419\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52419\" data-attachment-id=\"52419\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/05-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52419\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Decades of Horror\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52419\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Decades of Horror</p></div></p>\n<p>Film horor yang sumber kengeriannya berasal dari fakto-faktor alam atau mahluk hidup yang mana tadinya jinak, berubah menjadi sangat ganas dan menghabisi seluruh orang-orang dan sekitarnya</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Jaws, The Birds, Piranha, Bats, Lake Placid, Black Water</em></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/review-the-meg-dan-pandangan-yang-salah-terhadap-hiu/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Review The Meg dan Pandangan yang Salah Terhadap Hiu</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Psychological Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52420\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52420\" data-attachment-id=\"52420\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/06-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52420\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: IFC Center\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52420\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: IFC Center</p></div></p>\n<p>Mungkin kita sering mendengar <em>genre </em>ini. Tapi sayangnya kita masih kerap bingung untuk menentukan apakah film horor yang kita sakikan masuk ke dalam <em>genre psychological horror </em>atau tidak sama sekali.</p>\n<p>Oke akan saya jelaskan. Gampangnya begini saja. Apabila film horor tersebut menampilkan rasa ketakutannya melalui emosi yang dirasakan oleh karakternya atau film ini membuat kita langsung merinding sendiri dengan aura dan keadaan sekitar yang ditampilkan terlebih, dibantu lagi dengan aluna <em>scoring </em>musik yang mengerikan, maka film horor tersebut termasuk <em>psychological horror</em>.</p>\n<p>Dan umumnya, film jenis ini menampilkan sosok manusia sebagai sumber horornya. Sangat jarang sekali mahluk halus yang menjadi sumbernya.</p>\n<p>Terkecuali, apabila film tersebut dari awal terus menampilkan <em>build-up </em>merinding yang meresahkan sebelum akhirnya menampilkan mahluk halusnya, maka yap. Bisa dikatakan film horor yang kalian saksikan adalah <em>psychological horror</em>.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>The Shining, Rosemary’s Baby, The Uninvited, Get Out</em>.</p>\n<h3><strong>Slasher</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52421\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52421\" data-attachment-id=\"52421\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/07-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52421\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Bustle\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52421\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Bustle</p></div></p>\n<p>Horor yang fokus kisahnya menampilkan pembunuhan berantai entah korban-korbannya sudah direncanakan atau acak (<em>random</em>).</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Scream, Halloween, Texas Chainsaw Massacre, Halloween, Child’s Play, A Nightmare on the Elm Street</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Splatter</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52422\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52422\" data-attachment-id=\"52422\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/08-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52422\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Bloody Disgusting\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52422\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Bloody Disgusting</p></div></p>\n<p>Horor yang menampilkan banyak kekerasan grafis (<em>graphic violence</em>) seperti mutilasi, darah berlebihan, dan tampilan-tampilan sadistik lainnya.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Saw, The Human Centipede, Maniac, Hostel, Blood Feast</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Horror Thriller</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52423\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52423\" data-attachment-id=\"52423\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/09-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52423\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: No Film School\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52423\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: No Film School</p></div></p>\n<p>Serupa dengan <em>psychological horror</em>, banyak dari kita yang kerap mendengar sub-<em>genre </em>ini namun, masih suka bingung sendiri dengan <em>genre </em>ini.</p>\n<p>Jadi begini. <em>Horror thriller </em>adalah jenis film horor yang menampilkan elemen-elemen horor seperti monster, pembunuh, hantu, dll namun dengan pembangunan tensi takut yang sangat intens seperti <em>genre thriller</em>.</p>\n<p>Kalau misalkan kita hanya merasa tegang dan kaget saja, maka film yang kalian saksikan masih dalam rana <em>thriller</em>.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Don’t Breathe, Silence of the Lambs, The Invitation, Joy Ride, A Quiet Place</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Supernatural Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52424\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52424\" data-attachment-id=\"52424\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/10-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"10-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52424\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: The Wrap\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52424\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: The Wrap</p></div></p>\n<p>Horor yang kerap menampilkan sekaligus menggabungkan elemen-elemen berbau mistis bahkan keagamaan. Film ini kerpa menampilkan iblis (<em>demon</em>), arwah gentayangan, penyihir, dan peristiwa kesurupan.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>The Conjuring, Insidious, The Ring, the Grudge, it, The Exorcist, Suspiria, The Blair Witch Project</em></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/conjuring-cinematic-universe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Pantaskah Serial Horor Conjuring Dibuat Cinematic Universe-nya?</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Gothic Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52425\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52425\" data-attachment-id=\"52425\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/11-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"11-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52425\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Bloody Disgusting\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/11-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52425\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Bloody Disgusting</p></div></p>\n<p>Horor yang menggabungkan elemen horor dan elemen <em>gothic</em>. Terkadang di dalamnya juga terdapat unsur asmara (<em>romance</em>). <em>Genre </em>ini paling banyak ditampilkan di awal-awal zaman keemasan horor yaitu: 1920-1930.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Nosferatu, Dracula, The Phantom of the Opera, The Others, Crimson Peak</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Monster Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52426\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52426\" data-attachment-id=\"52426\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/12-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"12-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52426\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: The Verge\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/12-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52426\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: The Verge</p></div></p>\n<p>Horor  yang menampilkan monster yang membuat kekacauan dan bahkan membunuh siapapun di sekitarnya.  Sama seperti <em>gothic horror</em>, film ini pertama kali mencapai masa keemasannya di era 20 dan 30an.</p>\n<p>Khusus untuk Godzilla, film ini sebenarnya masuk juga ke <em>genre </em>ini. Tapi seiring berjalannya waktu, film-film Godzilla kerap dianggap sebagai <em>Kaiju Movie</em>.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Nosferatu, Dracula, Frankenstein, The Mummy, Godzilla, King Kong, A Quiet Place</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/quiet-place-sebuah-paku-tak-pernah-seseram-ini/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Quiet Place, Sebuah Paku Tak Pernah Seseram Ini</a></strong></p>\n<h3><strong>Found-Footage Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52427\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52427\" data-attachment-id=\"52427\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/13-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"13-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52427\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Mirror\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/13-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52427\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Mirror</p></div></p>\n<p>Film yang kerap juga disebut oleh kebanyakan <em>fans </em>horor di negeri kita, “film dokumenter” ini, adalah jenis film horor yang pengambilan gambarnya diambil secara langsung (<em>real-time</em>) oleh <em>camcorder </em>rumahan.</p>\n<p>Atau dengan kamera film pada umumnya Cuma diatur menjadi demikian. Umumnya horor tipe ini diproduksi agar dapat meyakinkan penontonnya kalau film horor yang sedang disaksikan benar-benar rekaman peristiwa yang pernah terjadi di dunia nyata.</p>\n<p>Padahal faktanya, hampir seluruh peristiwa di film <em>found footage </em>yang telah dirilis sejauh ini adalah 100% fiktif belaka.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Paranormal Activity, Blair Witch Project, REC, Devil’s Due, Cloverfield</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Cyber Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52428\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52428\" data-attachment-id=\"52428\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/14-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/14-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"14-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/14-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/14-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52428\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/14-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Variety\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/14-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/14-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52428\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Variety</p></div></p>\n<p>Bisa dikatakan <em>genre </em>ini adalah <em>genre </em>horor yang kini sedang <em>booming </em>di era internet, media sosial sekarang ini. Film ini berfokus pada peristiwa-peristiwa mengerikan yang diakibatkan oleh aktivitas tabu atau serangan gaib di media <em>online</em>.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>Unfriended, Friend Request, The Den</em></p>\n<h3><strong>Superhero Horror</strong></h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52429\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52429\" data-attachment-id=\"52429\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagai-jenis-film-horor/attachment/15-jenis-film-horor/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/15-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"15-jenis-film-horor\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/15-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/15-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52429\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/15-jenis-film-horor.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: CHOCILINO\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/15-jenis-film-horor.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/15-jenis-film-horor-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52429\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CHOCILINO</p></div></p>\n<p>Sama seperti <em>genre cyber horror</em>, <em>superhero horror</em> bisa dikatakan adalah <em>genre </em>horor yang kini sedang naik daun. Dan seperti namanya, <em>genre </em>ini menggabungkan elemen film horor dan film <em>superhero </em>yang kini masih  merajai industri perfilman Hollywood.</p>\n<p>Contoh: <em>The New Mutants, Brightburn</em><em> </em></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Nah itulah tadi 15 jenis<em> </em>film horor yang mungkin banyak dari kita belum terlalu ketahui. Semoga dengan seklumit pembahasan ini, ke depannya kita tidak akan salah mengidentifikasi lagi jenis film horor yang sedang kita saksikan.</p>\n<p>Dari 15 sub-<em>genre </em>horor ini, yang manakah yang merupakan favorit kalian?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4bcfa873-7868-522c-9b58-7f4a36203b16"}}}